<@U02F9CXTL> <@U0XJFPSRL> here are the steps in the podium invision as I'm imagining it for playtest, let me know if you see any red flags

Invision prototype steps

1. home screen
2. browse by location, starting at the US view
3. drill down into new york
4. open Coding in Queens
5. navigate back to location
6. navigate back to New Jersey (alternate path, navigate to home and drill down to New Jersey) 
7. open Methane Mapping with street view
8. back to home (alternate path - back button)
9. browse by tags
10. drill down on Culture
11. open Hidden Worlds of National Parks
12. back to home (alternate path - back button)
13 browse by tags
14. drill down on Coalition for Queens (no need to drill down on Coding in Queens project)
15. back to home (alternate path - back button)
16. drill down to search
17. drill down on Google Arts & Culture
